{"article_id":"ypjidns4gKRclFoP","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Obama announced the resignation of Chuck Hagel Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"commending the secretary of Defense for his `` steady hand '' through a period of transition for the United States ' military .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"Obama suggested","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"that it was Hagel 's decision","depth":11},{"id":5,"text":"to resign after less than two years in office ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"saying ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"`` If there 's one thing","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"I know about Chuck ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"it 's that he does not make this or any other decision lightly . ''","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Two Defense Department officials","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"speaking on condition of anonymity","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"Hagel had been under pressure from the White House on a variety of fronts ,","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"and that tension caused several discussions","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"that led to his resignation .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"The 68-year-old Hagel said","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"he will stay on the job `` every day , every moment ''","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"until his successor is nominated and confirmed by the Senate .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"`` It 's been the greatest privilege of my life","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to lead ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and most importantly , to serve , ''","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"Hagel said in an announcement from the White House Monday morning .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"Obama and Hagel made the announcement in the State Dining Room of the White House Monday morning , in front of about two dozen senior officials and Cabinet secretaries .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"Afterward , Hagel hugged Obama","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"and then turned toward the audience","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"and bowed .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Hagel arrived at the Pentagon in February 2013 during a period of belt-tightening and disengagement for the military ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"but ended up leading the fight against new and different enemies","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"- the Islamic State in Iraq and Syria , and the Ebola outbreak in western Africa .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"The announcement also comes","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"shortly as Obama approves plans","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"to give U.S. military commanders bigger roles alongside Afghanistan forces","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"as they fight the Taliban","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"following the end of the U.S. combat operation next month .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"A White House official said","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Hagel began speaking with Obama about departing the administration","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"beginning in October ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"noting","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"that the midterm congressional elections provided a natural transition .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Obama has also spoken to many top administration officials","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"about whether they would stay on for the last two years of his presidency ,","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"the official said .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Administration officials said","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"possibilities for Hagel 's job include Michèle Flournoy , a former undersecretary of Defense for policy","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"who was runner-up for the slot","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"when Obama tapped Hagel in early 2013 ;","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"Sen. Jack Reed , D-R.I. , a defense specialist and a former officer with the Army 's 82nd Airborne ; and Ashton Carter , a former deputy secretary of Defense .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Reed disavowed any interest .","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"`` Senator Reed loves his job","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"and wants to continue serving the people of Rhode Island in the United States Senate , ''","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"said press secretary Chip Unruh .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Discussions about Hagel began a few weeks ago","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"but picked up momentum Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"according to a senior Defense Department official","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"who was not authorized to speak publicly .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"By the weekend , the decision had been made","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"and there was concern","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"that it would leak out .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"Asked directly","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"whether Hagel was forced out ,","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"White House press secretary Josh Earnest said","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"`` the two of them arrived together '' at the decision .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"He noted","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that Hagel 's tenure is consistent with those of Obama 's two other Defense secretaries , Robert Gates and Leon Panetta .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"A series of foreign policy crises ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"including the rise of the Islamic State and the slow response to the Ebola epidemic ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"contributed to the need to for a change in senior personnel ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"the official said .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"Another senior Defense Department official said","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"Hagel did not clash with the White House on policy ,","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"nor was he stepping down in protest .","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"TheNew York Times ,","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"citing anonymous sources ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"first reported the resignation Monday .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Obama nominated Hagel in January 2013","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"to succeed Panetta .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"As a former senator from Nebraska","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"who had forged a friendship with Obama in the Senate ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Hagel became the only Republican on Obama 's national security team .","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"`` We come from different parties ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"but","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"in accepting this position ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"you sent a powerful message , especially to those in this city ,","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"when it comes to our national security and our military families ,","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"our country always comes first , ''","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Obama said Monday .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"Hagel got off to a rocky start","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"even before he was sworn in .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"His confirmation hearings before the Senate were contentious","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"- even with former colleagues from his own Republican Party .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Although relations with Capitol Hill improved over the last two years ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"Hagel still struggled to articulate Pentagon policies in briefings and speeches .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"`` Secretary Chuck Hagel and I have had our differences over many years ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"but I have always considered him a friend , a patriot , and a dedicated public servant","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"who has always put our country first and the needs of our men and women in uniform above his own , ''","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"Sen. John McCain , R-Ariz. , said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"that Hagel was frustrated by the administration 's national security policy and decision-making process ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"and that Defense secretaries have been micro-managed by the Obama White House .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"The Defense secretary had planned a trip to Asia ,","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"including a scheduled stop in Vietnam","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"that had personal meaning for Hagel .","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"When it was canceled earlier this month ,","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"Pentagon sources said","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"the change signaled trouble for Hagel 's tenure","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"but officials from the White House and Pentagon immediately denied","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"that Hagel was considering leaving or being pushed to step down .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"Hagel was the first enlisted combat veteran","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"to serve as secretary of Defense","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"-- a quality","depth":7},{"id":113,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Obama said","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"made him particularly attuned to the needs of servicemembers and their families .","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"`` He 's been in the dirt .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"He 's been in the mud .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"And that has established a special bond .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"He sees himself in them .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"They see themselves in him . ''","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Obama said .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"`` He volunteered for Vietnam","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"and still has the scars and shrapnel from the battles","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"he has fought . ''","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Obama will be the first president since Harry Truman","depth":6},{"id":126,"text":"to have four Defense secretaries during his time in office .","depth":6},{"id":127,"text":"The position was created during Truman 's tenure in 1947 .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":255,"left":0,"right":254,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":254,"left":198,"right":253,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":153,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"l